high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the sofa.
Pick the knife from the sofa.
Turn right to the coffee table.
Place the knife on the coffee table.
Turn left near the sofa.
Pick the knife from the sofa.
Turn right to the coffee table.
Place the knife on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: To place the knife on the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk straight to reach the sofa
Take a knife from the sofa
Turn left and take few steps and again take a right turn to reach the coffee table on the right side
Put the knife on the coffee table
Turn right and take few steps and turn left to reach the sofa again
Take one more knife from the sofa
Turn left and take few steps and again take a right turn to reach the coffee table again
Put the knife on the left lower bottom of the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Put the knife on the coffee table

high_descs: Go straight ahead to the sofa.
Look at the two knives on the sofa, and pick up the one closer to the side of the sofa, the one nearest the blue pillow on the side.
Turn towards the coffee table in front of the sofa.
Place the knife down on the coffee table.
Go back towards the sofa.
Pick up the second knife from the sofa.
Go back to the coffee table.
Place the second knife down next to the first.
anns.task_desc: Place two knives down on a coffee table.
